summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to portions of Blocks 29 and 36, Little City Farms, Division No. 5, a portion of Block 1, Bliss Gardens Addition; a portion of Block 2, Powell's 2nd Addition; a portion of Block 1, Hawks Addition; a portion of the southwest one-quarter of Section 36, township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M. and a portion of the northwest one-quarter of Section 36, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M. for street purposes and laying off 25th Avenue Southwest, Southwest Barton Street and Southwest Kenyon Street. (Southwest Trenton Street, et al; Paving, etc.)
